# Steps to install SASS

# 1. Installed Node Version Manager (nvm)
Already have nvm installed, so I just updated it to the latest version.
# nvm update
# nvm --version

# 2. Restarted terminal, then installed Node.js version 20.16.0
nvm install 20.16.0
nvm use 20.16.0

# 3. Installed SASS version 3.7.4
npm install sass
